The paper deals with salient object detection using deep learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the problem of salient object ranking, which involves developing metrics and benchmarks for evaluating algorithms, and this is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of datasets and data analysis, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
